author: mrmitch
title: my first and probably my only key chain
review: I got this in a S@H grab bag promotion years ago. I keep it with the collection but, it just sits there. Can't really play with it and don't want to risk losing it by putting to use as intended. Some folks collect them and I'm sure they would rate it much higher than myself.

author: KLOKRIECHER
title: LEGO Gear (Key Chains/Star Wars) - Luke Skywalker Key Chain Review
review:
This key chain is part of the LEGO Star Wars theme and the minifig we get is the original version of Luke Skywalker in his pilot uniform. It's a really cool minifig to have as a key chain but the only problems I have with those is that you're not able to take off the legs, the head or the headgear.

Pros

  • Minifig looks cool

Cons

  • Legs, head and/or headgear don't come off

Summary

All in all it's a great set to get and I would HIGHLY recommend you to get this. You can find this set on eBay, BrickLink and Amazon for sure.
